<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Cost2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Cost,</orth> vb., to be bought at the expense of; with an accus., or a dative and accus.: <bibl n="shak. luc 146" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 146</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 159</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.1.123" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. III, 1, 123</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.90" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 90</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.387" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 387</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 2, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.1.88" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 1, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 5.2.128" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. V, 2, 128</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.5.11" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 5, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.1.12" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 1, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.134" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 3, 134</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.268" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 268</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.177" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 177</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.223" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 223</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.8.2" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 8, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.217" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 217</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.259" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 259</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3.173" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. V, 3, 173</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.93" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.6.81" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 6, 81</bibl>. <cit><quote>it will c. thee dear,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.255" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 255</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>what she doth c. the holding,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 2.2.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 2, 51</bibl></cit>. 